desc = [[%LOCATIONMETHOD% an artillery platoon shelling the city of Antakya with little regard for civilians, inflicting severe losses on our troops, including friendly coalition troops and the 5th Armored Brigade. To reduce further losses, command has prioritized the destruction of this battery.

