Secondary objective: Eliminate enemy supply trucks and other support assets.

Threats: AAA, short range SAMs, be advised there's enemy SHORAD elements inside Antakya, west and north of the artillery battery, and at least 2 patrol craft on the coast bombarding some of our friendly positions.

